# Archive

This directory indexes retired or superseded material for `<repo-name>`.

## Belongs Here

- non-current documentation kept for record
- superseded guidance preserved for traceability
- retired structure notes that should not be treated as current

## Does Not Belong Here

- current canonical guidance: `../Architecture/`
- active proposals: `../Proposals/`
- active migration work: `../Migrations/`
- current reference material still in use: `../Reference/`

## Use

Use this subtree for material that remains worth keeping but is no longer
authoritative.
